这些黑暗时期为世界开怀大笑而受到了人们的欢迎。如果您错过了这个故事，我会总结一下。上周，Google发布了Gemini，这是AI聊天机器人和图像生成器，旨在与Open AI和其他人的类似应用程序竞争。这几乎不是一个更重要的推出，而且几乎不会出错。</p><p>人们一开始玩它，他们就会注意到一些奇怪的东西。当他们询问它的历史人物图片时，无论背景如何，它都会构成“多样化”的图像。这是被要求寻找维京人（历史上最白人）的形象时发生的事情： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg" width="354" height="212.4" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;