p/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcc97f37f-3745-42f1-bb88-e2f59f024479_955x642.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcc97f37f-3745-42f1-bb88-e2f59f024479_955x642.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>最奇怪的是，当Gemini被要求为第二次世界大战纳粹的照片时，它提供了美丽的种族和性别彩虹，包括上面的绅士。<br><br>这些图像并不是一些恶作剧制造商在提示的情况下产生的。他们一次又一次地回答标准问题。这个问题不仅限于图像产生，而且不仅仅是多样性。双子座有一个非常独特的世界观（我正在使用过去的时态，因为为了响应Furore，Google暂停了其图像生成工具并绝育了聊天机器人）。我想您可以称其为Wake，但这并不能完全传达它的极端或多么愚蠢。这更像是有人表现出唤醒的粗暴模仿一样： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4d65a068-2cd8-4ff8-9862-6e78cc6a5d0b_896x536.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4d65a068-2cd8-4ff8-9862-6e78cc6a5d0b_896x536.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4d65a068-2cd8-4ff8-9862-6e78cc6a5d0b_896x536.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/http